          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A thin self-supporting target was prepared by",
                "evaporating ScBr(3) onto a carbon foil of 10 mug/cm**2",
                "and placed inside a goniometric chamber. A thin gold",
                "layer was evaporated on top of the Sc-Br layer in order",
                "to calculate the beam current and to ensure better",
                "thermal stability of the target during the irradiation.",
                "for energy range 2300-5500 keV",
                "The ScBr3 target was replaced by a thick approx. 0.2 cm",
                "pressed Sc(2)O(3) target. For this measurement the",
                "thick target was irradiated for proton energies in the",
                "range E(lab)=3100-5500 keV",
                "The target was found to consist of 10.6+-0.9 mug/cm**2",
                "Sc-45, 19+-2 mug/cm**2 of Br-nat",
                "and 9.1+-0.6 mug/cm**2 of Au-197"
              ]
            }
          ],
